title: Hey, where's my stuff!
message: Welcome Back Spartan. If you're reading this messge, you probably noticed that we took away your sweet credits, armors, vintage baseball card collection... Sorry about that.|n|nThose of you who have been hosting and keeeping this game alive have done so at the cost of your progression and we want to make it right! If you'd like a FAT credit boost or something else, Reach out to the team and we'd be happy to oblige.|n|nThank you for your continued support <3
